{
  "stem": "20084.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If I could smuggle out some-- some clothing from there, and-- and I could exchange for it potato or something, I was able to bake a potato in the-- in the-- in the hearth already.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I could manage to get something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyhow, I worked there for-- for-- for a little while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then this job came to an end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I got another job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then the war broke out with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then make the ghetto smaller.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That were-- there was a lot of grabbing people at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then with the dogs and shooting, and-- and-- and this was constantly going out, just to keep us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Killing was a daily routine, the killing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then I got another job when the war broke out with Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was the other side of the river, Vistula.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were going down there at night, in the evening, through the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We worked at night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were bringing-- this was, already I think, 1942, in winter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were bringing German from the Russian front, frozen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Frozen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were bringing in, at night, with the Red Cross, with Red Cross trains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they were-- they had typhus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They has lice, the big of my thumb and this was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know what's [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is to delouse them, to do the steam-- the steam and the showers and the baths, and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And this was-- this was on a side of a railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we had to carry them from the trains that they brought in from the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were moaning and groaning down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There were injured and so forth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But most of them were young and frozen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we used to carry them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "There was no platform.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
